And people are arising in the
Middle East, they're arising

00:52:27.945 --> 00:52:29.313 align:middle line:90%
in France, for example.

00:52:29.313 --> 00:52:30.414 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: Yes.

00:52:30.414 --> 00:52:32.984 align:middle line:84%
>> CS: In America --
the number of nonprofits

00:52:32.984 --> 00:52:37.288 align:middle line:84%
