00:52:38.689 --> 00:52:39.857 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: Yes, very much so.

00:52:39.857 --> 00:52:41.792 align:middle line:84%
>> CS: Yes, they're
saying let's get involved,

00:52:41.792 --> 00:52:44.228 align:middle line:84%
protecting animals,
protecting the environment,

00:52:44.228 --> 00:52:47.331 align:middle line:84%
working for justice,
working to free prisoners.

00:52:47.331 --> 00:52:53.337 align:middle line:84%
I mean nonprofits have increased
by millions and that's in Africa

00:52:53.337 --> 00:52:55.139 align:middle line:90%
and America, everywhere.

00:52:55.139 --> 00:52:57.375 align:middle line:84%
That says we need to
notice that phenomena,

00:52:57.375 --> 00:52:59.410 align:middle line:84%
something is happening
in the world.

