larger,

00:53:14.458 --> 00:53:15.860 align:middle line:90%
this whole comment they made.

00:53:15.860 --> 00:53:18.829 align:middle line:84%
>> CS: Yes, yes, that was a very
sweet story, a very sweet story.

00:53:18.829 --> 00:53:23.134 align:middle line:84%
