coming together of spirituality

00:53:34.211 --> 00:53:36.881 align:middle line:84%
with solidarity and
social justice,

00:53:36.881 --> 00:53:39.884 align:middle line:84%
to promote that marriage, that
Andrew Harvey speaks about,

00:53:39.884 --> 00:53:41.285 align:middle line:90%
Matthew Fox and so many others.

00:53:41.285 --> 00:53:42.520 align:middle line:90%
>> RM: Yes.

00:53:42.520 --> 00:53:45.990 align:middle line:84%
>> CS: So we have different
programs and we publish

00:53:45.990 --> 00:53:49.193 align:middle line:84%
and we teach and we do campuses,
we invite people, like Andrew

00:53:49.193 --> 00:53:52.763 align:middle line:84%
and Matthew Fox and others
to come and speak there.

00:53:52.763 --> 00:53:54.665 align:middle line:84%
But that story was
so fascinating

00:53:54.665 --> 00:53:56.701 align:middle line:84%
because I was staying,
working late,

00:53:56.701 --> 00:54:00.338 align:middle line:84%
and then I heard a
knock on the door.

00:54:00.338 --> 00:54:05.076 align:middle line:84%
And, you know, I looked and I
saw this couple of young people,

00:54:05.076 --> 00:54:07.445 align:middle line:84%
and they were very young,
probably in their 20s,

00:54:07.445 --> 00:54:11.582 align:middle line:84%
and they just looked wonderful,
and energy and excitement and,

00:54:11.582 --> 00:54:13.384 align:middle line:84%
you know, and I opened it --
I said, how can I help you?

00:54:13.384 --> 00:54:15.920 align:middle line:84%
They said, oh, we just saw
the name, Olive Branch Center,

00:54:15.920 --> 00:54:17.154 align:middle line:84%
and we wanted to know
what's that about?

00:54:17.154 --> 00:54:19.023 align:middle line:90%
I said, sure, come in.

00:54:19.023 --> 00:54:21.659 align:middle line:84%
So I came in and I gave
them my minute speech

00:54:21.659 --> 00:54:25.763 align:middle line:84%
around the importance of
spirituality and solidarity

00:54:25.763 --> 00:54:29.400 align:middle line:84%
and social justice and
inclusion to come more together,

00:54:29.400 --> 00:54:30.801 align:middle line:84%
and they looked at
me and they said

00:54:30.801 --> 00:54:34.305 align:middle line:84%
with these bright beautiful
eyes, and they said,

00:54:34.305 --> 00:54:39.210 align:middle line:84%
you mean it wasn't like that or
it's not something like this?

00:54:39.210 --> 00:54:40.378 align:middle line:90%
Of course, I mean it was

00:54:40.378 --> 00:54:43.247 align:middle line:84%
like why are you telling
me this new kind of --

00:54:43.247 --> 00:54:45.583 align:middle line:84%
yes, of course, I
mean I never expected.

00:54:45.583 --> 00:54:48.753 align:middle line:84%
They go [inaudible]
relationship of my life.

00:54:48.753 --> 00:54:50.354 align:middle line:84%
>> RM: Isn't that
how it's always been?

00:54:50.354 --> 00:54:52.156 align:middle line:84%
>> CS: Exactly, and how
it supports everybody,

00:54:52.156 --> 00:54:54.191 align:middle line:84%
and that is how it's
supposed to be.

00:54:54.191 --> 00:54:57.194 align:middle line:84%
They said we are spiritual,
and telling me about involved

00:54:57.194 --> 00:54:59.430 align:middle line:84%
in this and that, and
we expect to be involved

00:54:59.430 --> 00:55:00.798 align:middle line:90%
and our friends are involved.

00:55:00.798 --> 00:55:03.067 align:middle line:84%
And I said thank you, and I
said to them, you know, what,

00:55:03.067 --> 00:55:06.670 align:middle line:84%
coming from Lebanon the
children of the war thank you

00:55:06.670 --> 00:55:08.806 align:middle line:84%
because you are the
answer of their prayer.

00:55:08.806 --> 00:55:12.309 align:middle line:84%
They have prayed for you, they
have prayed for people like you

00:55:12.309 --> 00:55:16.013 align:middle line:84%
who will make the stand for
peace, who will make the stand

00:55:16.013 --> 00:55:18.983 align:middle line:84%
with the courage
and the passion,

00:55:18.983 --> 00:55:20.351 align:middle line:90%
and that you are heroes.

00:55:20.351 --> 00:55:23.621 align:middle line:84%
So I was able to really honor
them, but I was very touched

00:55:23.621 --> 00:55:25.356 align:middle line:90%
by their response, very touched.

